  <md:title>Solve Equations with Variables and Constants on Both Sides</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Solve an equation with constants on both sides</item>
<item>Solve an equation with variables on both sides</item>
<item>Solve an equation with variables and constants on both sides</item>
