    <entry><media id="eip-id1168184848828" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_02_03_004g_img_new.jpg"/></media></entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry namest="c1" nameend="c2"/>
    <entry>The variables are now on one side and the constants on the other.<newline/>We continue from here as we did earlier.</entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry namest="c1" nameend="c2">Divide both sides by 8.</entry>
    <entry><media id="eip-id1168184848861" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_02_03_004h_img_new.jpg"/></media></entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry namest="c1" nameend="c2">Simplify.</entry>
    <entry><media id="eip-id1168184848881" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_02_03_004i_img_new.jpg"/></media></entry>
