  </row>
  <row>
    <entry valign="bottom" namest="c1" nameend="c2">Divide both sides by <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> to make <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> the coefficient of <m:math><m:mi>a</m:mi></m:math>.</entry>
